{"tid":1735823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府有心想打殘勇武派，依家 棄守理工大學各自歸家，得罪講句到時兩個差佬都可以逐個逐個拉曬你哋","createTime":"2019-11-18T15:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T16:12:37.000Z","uid":202340,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"685a35d5bbb72ac8588010ec2585c8416ecf2f5e","tid":1735823,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"<em>董卓之入洛陽，詡以太尉掾爲平津都尉，遷討虜校尉。卓壻中郎將牛輔屯陝，詡在輔軍。卓敗，輔又死，衆恐懼，校尉李傕、郭汜、張濟等欲解散，間行歸鄉里。詡曰：「聞長安中議欲盡誅涼州人，而諸君棄衆單行，即一亭長能束君矣。不如率衆而西，所在收兵，以攻長安，爲董公報仇，幸而事濟，奉國家以征天下，若不濟，走未後也。」</em><br />\n<br />\n同樣道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要走嘅話差佬打到入嚟先走都未遲 反正拉到都係告"},{"pid":"442455990d1ff4cc97e6e08294f9e70662e8b41c","tid":1735823,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:51:30.000Z","msg":"冇錯，唔好中計，老鼠成想領功架揸"},{"pid":"d73f51a3c36e05a5776c67586640ee660759b027","tid":1735823,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbf07573b24ab9d68f012c7c6262881459ac369b","tid":1735823,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"唔好信曾鈺成佢地，保皇黨無個好人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e13972c93af1fb27614738a9d8521e4ff9d333a","tid":1735823,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf07573b24ab9d68f012c7c6262881459ac369b","tid":1735823,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"唔好信曾鈺成佢地，保皇黨無個好人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"講真各自返到屋企 最多都係舒舒服服畀你瞓一日 第日肯定有差佬拉你"},{"pid":"efe3ac40fecd6bf44e957ffa09e7c17a9a418e9b","tid":1735823,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e139